{
  "stem": "4187.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a rather interesting journey, in that we really saw Germany collapse.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this was April.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we truly did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We saw-- we went through-- one of the places I remember very clearly was Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was absolutely nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were some walls standing, but behind the walls, there was nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, every time we saw one of these buildings, how wonderful, how wonderful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Every time we heard a siren, we said, wonderful, wonderful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Naturally, did this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as we were taken through Germany, we saw soldiers without-- without proper clothing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We saw them literary running the-- away from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Well, the Russians were still pretty far, but all the same, they were all going up west as  far as they could.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we saw civilians in incredible-- By the way, I must say-- I must tell you that people are saying that the Germans didn't know.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In Belsen, the camp was terribly near the little town, so near that from the camp, from a particular corner, you could actually see a bridge, which was just a little bridge in-- in-- in the little-- little town.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And civilians, when we went-- when they-- when they took us for a shower, which wasn't often, the shower area was sort of near the end of the camp.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We saw civilians walking outside.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they saw us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They saw us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only in Duderstadt we had a few-- a few nasty-- but no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, they didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they saw us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Belsen was part of that little town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they're saying they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] It's so ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is so bizarre that anyone can argue and believe that they didn't know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, that's just by the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I just remembered that.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
